WeaponReady (script event)
==========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Enables the ability of the weapon to fire.

Usage
-----

*void* weaponReady()

Parameters
----------

This event does not accept parameters.

